{
  "title": "Malty Juicy Algerian Tomato Tagine",
  "description": "A romantic Algerian dish featuring confit tomatoes and mayonnaise, this malty and juicy tagine is perfect for a special occasion. It is also raw-friendly and can be served as a snack or light meal.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
